  "response": "There could be several reasons why you might be experiencing difficulty changing your profile picture on Quora via your phone:\n\n1. App version: Ensure you're using the latest version of the Quora app.\n\n2. Device compatibility: Some older phone models or operating systems might have limited functionality.\n\n3. App permissions: Check that Quora has permission to access your photos and camera.\n\n4. Technical glitch: The app might be experiencing a temporary issue.\n\n5. Browser limitations: If you're using a mobile browser, it might not support profile picture changes.\n\nTo troubleshoot:\n- Update the Quora app\n- Restart the app\n- Check your device's permissions\n- Try logging out and logging back in\n- If all else fails, try changing your profile picture from a desktop browser\n\nIf the problem persists, you may want to contact Quora support directly for specific assistance.",
